init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is devastated, and goes to the store to buy a new mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's the same one he got last year.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He looks at the price tag.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The clerk looks at the screen and says, "Sir, this mug is already registered to another customer."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Murray follows the clerk to the back of the store.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The clerk stopped in front of one of the curtains and pulled it back.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The clerk pulled the curtain aside and motioned for Murray to step inside.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He looked around the room, and then looked at the clerk.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "But, I want the same one I got last year.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry, sir, but that mug is already registered to another customer.
